Sounds like a mixture of the sc file format and BASIC:<p><pre><code>    let A0 = 123 
    let A1 = 234 
    let A2 = 345 
    rightstring B3 = &quot;asd&quot;
    leftstring B5 = &quot;foo&quot;
    label B11 = &quot;bar&quot;
    goto B11 A0
</code></pre>
Just a textual description of what your spreadsheet should look like. Gosling had it right back in the 80s ;)
